Chat Edit: 'This is not changing the wallpaper even though you are saying it did:

swww img ~/Pictures/Wallpapers/Gruvbox/default.jpg --transition-type grow --transition-pos 0.5,0.5 --transition-duration 2 && sleep 3 && swww query

If the change is logged somewhere, that log is incorrect. I suspect something may be getting overwritten because the user can slo use manual wallpaper selection via waypaper. '
